The National Vice Chairman (South East) of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) Chief Ali Odefa has advised governorship aspirants in Anambra State to spend their money wisely by lobbying delegates to the party primaries instead of the National Working Committee(NWC) whose members have no voting power. Odefa offered the advice in the PDD south east zonal stakeholders meeting in Awka.What is important, Odefa said is that the most popular aspirant wins the primaries in an honest and transparent manner. He said he had to offer the advice because every aspirant is capable of governing the state. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! He said that with two senators, six House of Representatives members and six House of Assembly members winning on the ticket of PDP is enough to win the governorship seat.He appealed party members who still have cases in court to withdraw them because “if we work together we will be in Government House next year”. He also appealed to party members to donate to the party to enable it have enough resources to shoulder its responsibilities. S. African Health Union Urges Gov’t To Be Transparent On Vaccine Plan JUST IN: Saudi Arabia ‘To Open Airspace, Land, Sea Border’ With Qatar He also spoke about Governor David Umahi leaving the party, saying his exit had no effect. Earlier in his speech the state chairman of the party Chief Ndubisi Nwobu said that the PDP is a happy and united family and assured of a transparent and fair primaries. He observed that politics is about give and take as no one can do it alone. Nwobu urged the aspirants to have absolute confidence in the state executive committee to do right to every one of them. In response, a former governor of Anambra State and Vice-Presidential candidate of the party in the 2019 election, Mr. Peter Obi announced a monthly donation of N4 million to the party, and N100, 000.00 to each of the 326 wards in the state. He volunteered to lead the party on a membership drive in the state.At the end of the meeting resolved that the party primaries must be free and fair, the aspirants must go to the field and make it vibrant and that members should withdraw all court cases SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION